3. Add '-e NNNN' to the SHELLCHECK_OPTS setting in your .yml action file.

https://github.com/apache/doris/blob/500c7fb702cd9a13e4079d8c8c59e78294c4006d/fe/fe-core/src/main/java/org/apache/doris/external/elasticsearch/EsUtil.java#L168

1. This is my “mapping” configuration，Contains fields such as "dynamic", "runtime"

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2849902/211778946-dfda74da-e566-4bf3-bb67-26fb1fd9eda7.png)


2. So here's the problem, when the first field isn't “properties”, it's a problem

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2849902/211777519-fb4e29cc-9d68-4567-888d-c476303cd93b.png)

This will return other  wrong  fields in “mappings”.


**I will fix this later, if I can** @stalary
